title: Buckethead_Bucketheadland2
description:
Bucketheadland 2 is the sequel to Buckethead&#039;s first album Bucketheadland, a theme album about his fictional "abusement" park[1]. The album is also his 10th full length album.


The song "Slaughter Zone Exit" contains a hidden track.
